[I] A fast, lightweight and minimalistic Wayland terminal emulator

[T] The fast, lightweight and minimalistic Wayland terminal emulator.
[T] Features: Fast (see benchmarks, and performance),
[T] lightweight (in dependencies, on-disk and in-memory), wayland native,
[T] on-the-fly font resize/DPI adjustment, color emoji support, multi-seat,
[T] server/daemon mode, sixel image support, scrollback search, DE agnostic.

[U] https://codeberg.org/dnkl/foot

[A] Daniel Eklöf
[M] NoTag <notag@t2sde.org>

[C] extra/x11
[F] CROSS CUSTOM-LTO

[L] MIT
[V] 1.27.0

[D] be6d41364f8121307c763d44b562758c7f0d2d8f2e584dd43d50cfd5 foot-1.27.0.tar.gz https://codeberg.org/dnkl/foot/releases/download/1.27.0/

rungpepinstall=0

var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dtests=false
var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dterminfo=disabled
[ "$SDECFG_DEBUG" = 1 ] || var_append mesonopt ' ' --buildtype=release
[ "$SDECFG_LTO" = 1 ] || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Db_lto=false
